flowchart TD
    A[Incoming Client Request] --> B[FastAPI Gateway]
    B --> C{Any Healthy Backends?}

    C -- No --> D[Return 503 Service Unavailable]
    C -- Yes --> E[Read Round Robin Pointer]

    E --> F[Select Next Healthy Backend]
    F --> G[Advance Pointer]
    G --> H[Forward Request to Selected Backend]

    H --> I{Backend Response Successful?}
    I -- Yes --> J[Return Response to Client]
    I -- No --> K{Retry Attempts Remaining?}

    K -- No --> L[Return Final Error Response]
    K -- Yes --> M[Exclude Failed Backend]
    M --> N{Another Healthy Backend Available?}

    N -- No --> L
    N -- Yes --> F

    J --> O[Record Request Metrics]
    L --> O
    O --> P[Persist Request History in Supabase]
    P --> Q[Publish Live API Lifecycle Event]
    Q --> R[Update Angular Observability Dashboard]
